(f_n) \text{ is Cauchy in measure } \Leftrightarrow (f_n) \text{ is Cauchy in } L_0(D,d) \text { and }
 d(f_n,f) \rightarrow 0 \Leftrightarrow f_n \rightarrow f \text{ in measure}
